Versatile Card.   

@jsttu Please do a search with the advanced options to see all the cards with with 1 power this card could block on the first turn for you. Also, please do a search for all the cards that can deal 1 damage to a creature. A [prodigal wizard](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=prodigal wizard) holds a [Royal assassin](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name= Royal assassin) at bay, but not this guy. As others have stated, the mercenary search ability is fantastic, it's the support that is bad. If I'm going to grade a card/ability of a card, I go off it's potential. Unfortunately, one 4 star card (which is what I gave it) doesn't make a good deck when the rest of the cards you'd have to place with it are 1 and 2 star cards. Instead it collects dust until some 3-5 star cards are around to supplement. That's the difference between individual card strength and deck strength.   

I'm not saying your comment was outlandish, but it was overly eccentric.

